Task Management App
Overview
This is a React Native application designed to help users manage their tasks. The app features a friendly user interface for viewing and searching through tasks, organized into various categories.

Features
Task Overview: Displays a greeting and the number of tasks for the day.
Profile Image: Includes a profile picture.
Search Bar: Allows users to search for tasks.
Categories: Lists task categories with descriptions and images.
Ongoing Tasks: Shows a list of ongoing tasks.
Custom Components: Utilizes custom components throughout the application.
